        <p class="body-tactical text-white font-thin text-sm">
          Permanent digital profile for fast remakes and future upgrades. Your ear geometry is stored securely for life.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black/55 p-8 rounded-lg text-center border-2" style="border-color: rgb(108, 104, 70);">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
