        </svg>
        <h3 class="subheading-tactical text-white text-xl mb-4">Future-Proof Platform</h3>
        <p class="body-tactical text-white font-thin text-sm">
          Ready for advanced biometrics and health monitoring as your operational needs evolve.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/technology"
        ><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 btn-scarlet cta-tactical px-8 py-4 text-base rounded-sm">
          See How It Works
